| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1749 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 59fc6ebb-bb3b-5255-9970-899e2df4a4bd"
